{"type": "article", "id": 14232, "title": "可折叠的圆桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-01T06:36:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000324t8ajlO7HIQcgXDs0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t偏爱小型物件的 COS 和 Hay 一起邀请了西班牙设计师 Tomas Alonso ，设计了一套可折叠的圆桌。有“高瘦”型和“矮胖”型两款。圆桌只有三只腿，其中一根带颜色的圆柱杆连接了另外两根木腿，同时伸出桌面，起到稳定的作用。不需要用时把它收起来立在墙边，简单方便。圆桌可以选择青灰色或白色杆两种，与浅色木纹搭配，十分清爽。<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/08/28/cos-hay-collaboration-tomas-alonso-folding-wooden-tables/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141834rub0KRLD4WTG76Z9.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"514\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0982906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141834h0eTPLIjZcQMYo9a.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141835PZQgpoJUxMtbVvaC.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"571\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.22008547\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261418350kJhO73nKsr2BmIA.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}